 %   \mathcal{M}\left(\smax\right)=\left\{ \mathbb{P}\xz \left\{  \sum_{l=1}^L \gamma_l \mathbb{P}_{Y \mid X}^{(l)} + \gamma_{L+1} \sum_{l=1}^L \eta_l(X) \mathbb{P}_{Y \mid X}^{(l)}\right\} \mid \gamma \in \mathcal{S}(\smax) \right\}
